#

Crispy Baked Potato Chips

40 min
$3.5
150 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Snack

Tags:

SnackEasyHealthy

Description

Enjoy these light and crispy baked potato chips, a healthier alternative to fried snacks!

Ingredients

  • russet potatoes: 2 large
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • paprika: 1/2 teaspoon
  • garlic powder: 1/2 teaspoon
